                    <tr>
                        
                        <td colspan="8" class="cellpadding_top_5">
                            <p class="left_indent_0 first_line_indent_24 align_justified">The
                                particulars to be given above of freeboards and allowances for fresh
                                water are to be taken from the load line certificate currently in
                                force in respect of the ship. Paragraphs referring to freeboards
                                which the certificate shows have not been assigned to the ship must
                                be deleted.</p>
